; UNSAT: 2-bit counter starting at 0, incrementing by 2 (always even).
; Bad: counter == 1 (never reachable: counter visits {0, 2, 0, 2, ...})
; Expected: UNSAT (within BMC bound)
1 sort bitvec 2
2 sort bitvec 1
3 state 1 cnt
4 zero 1
5 init 1 3 4
6 constd 1 2
7 add 1 3 6
8 next 1 3 7
9 one 1
10 eq 2 3 9
11 bad 10
